
## 📄 SQL Queries

The SQL queries used for KPI calculations, sales trend analysis, category-wise performance evaluation, and identification of top/bottom performing pizzas are included in this repository.

📂 File: [PIZZA SALES SQL QUERIES.docx](PIZZA%20SALES%20SQL%20QUERIES.docx)

### Analysis Covered
- Total Revenue
- Total Orders
- Total Pizzas Sold
- Average Order Value
- Average Pizzas Per Order
- Daily & Monthly Sales Trends
- Sales by Pizza Category
- Sales by Pizza Size
- Top & Bottom Performing Pizzas
